<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbdf23077-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s7140"><num value="7140">§ 7140.</num><heading> Leasing Liaison Committee; establishment; composition</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is established a Leasing Liaison Committee which shall be composed of an equal number of members appointed by the Secretary and the Secretary of the Interior.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbdf23078-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/95/91/tII/s210">Pub. L. 95–91, title II, § 210</ref>, <date date="1977-08-04">Aug. 4, 1977</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/91/577">91 Stat. 577</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
